  product;
- sell, rent, lease, sublicense, or commercially distribute the Software as a
  standalone product;
- use the Software to provide paid hosted knowledge-base, capture, search,
  wiki, agent-memory, or retrieval services to third parties;
- remove, obscure, or alter copyright notices, license notices, product names,
  or attribution notices;
- claim that this project is open source;
- use the name "Sift" or confusingly similar branding for an unauthorized
  commercial product, hosted service, or derivative;
- use the Software in a way that violates applicable law or infringes third
  party rights.

4. Distribution

You may share unmodified copies of the Software for personal, educational,
research, or evaluation purposes, provided that:

- this license file is included;
- copyright notices are preserved;
- the recipient is informed that the Software is source-available, not open
