Distribution of modified versions requires prior written permission unless the
distribution is limited to private Internal Use within Your own organization.

5. Commercial and Hosted Use

Commercial use that is limited to Internal Use is allowed.

Commercial use that offers Sift or a derivative to third parties as a Hosted
